          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>We don't know when--or if--a new Mega Man game will ever be released, but we do know that the adventures of this Capcom icon do make for some great reading. In case you missed it, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">the first volume of Little Mega Man</a> was released a few months ago, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Little-Mega-Man-2/dp/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">and the second volume</a> is scheduled to arrive on August 19. These are cute and surprisingly hilarious manga strips that star Mega Man during his early days, and they feature some fantastic art.</p><div title="6532124 -- Little Mega Man Volumes 1 and 2" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3653" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6532124 -- Little Mega Man Volumes 1 and 2" data-collection="">                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20">Little Mega Man Volume One</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$14</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>Little Mega Man Volume One is 196 pages in size, is illustrated by Yukito, and written by Yuushi Kawata. The duo had previously collaborated Mr. Mega Man--a gag manga that reimagines as an adult trying to lead a peaceful life as a dentist--and Little Mega Man is another fun spin on the character. </p>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Little-Mega-Man-2/dp/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Little-Mega-Man-2\/dp\/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Little-Mega-Man-2/dp/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20">Little Mega Man Volume Two</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Little-Mega-Man-2/dp/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Little-Mega-Man-2\/dp\/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Little-Mega-Man-2/dp/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20">$14 | Releases August 19</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>Little Mega Man Volume Two amplifies the absurdity of the manga, as the Blue Bomber takes on strange new foes--like Demon Man, Sushi Man, and Plasma TV Man--meets his European counterpart, and even runs into his future self, Mega Man X.  </p>                      </div>   </div><p>These official English localizations have been produced by publisher Udon Entertainment in collaboration with Capcom, a company you might recognize for its other licensed works in the Street Fighter franchise.</p><p>As mentioned above, you can also grab <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943789?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;tag=gamespot-buybutton-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mr. Mega Man</a> to read all about the horrors of adulthood. Meanwhile, Mega Man's old sparring partners have also entered the workforce, resulting in Robot Masters now earning a decent living. Cut Man is a barber, Flame Man is a chef, and Top Man is an online influencer, but something sinister is lurking in the shadows.</p><p>For more traditional Mega Man adventures, there are several comic book trade paperbacks you can check out as well. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Mastermix-Robot-Rebellion/dp/1772940941?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man Mastermix: Robot Rebellion</a> is essentially a Year One story that follows Mega Man on his early missions, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Mastermix-Asteroid-Blues/dp/1772941018?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man Mastermix: Asteroid Blues</a> is an outer space adventure, and <a href="http://amazon.com/Mega-Man-Gigamix-Hitoshi-Ariga/dp/1926778235?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man: Gigamix</a> is a globetrotting adventure as the blue hero takes on several of Dr. Wily's nefarious bots. Mega Man fans can also grab a delightful tribute to the character with <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Tribute-UDON/dp/1927925673?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man Tribute</a>. This is a compilation of artwork from illustrators all over the world, paying tribute to the legacy of the character and his various games.</p><h2>Mega Man book deals</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943797?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Little Mega Man Volume One</a> -- $14</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Little-Mega-Man-2/dp/1772943851?tag=gamespot-preorders-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Little Mega Man Volume Two</a> -- $14 | Releases August 19</li><li><a href="http://amazon.com/Mega-Man-Gigamix-Hitoshi-Ariga/dp/1926778235?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man: Gigamix Volume 1</a> -- $13</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Gigamix-Hitoshi-Ariga/dp/1926778278?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man: Gigamix Volume 2</a> -- $30</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Mastermix-Robot-Rebellion/dp/1772940941?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man: Mastermix - Robot Rebellion</a> -- $18 ($20)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Mastermix-Asteroid-Blues/dp/1772941018?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man: Mastermix - Asteroid Blues</a> -- $16</li><li><a title="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Tribute-UDON/dp/1927925673" href="https://www.amazon.com/Mega-Man-Tribute-UDON/dp/1927925673?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mega Man Tribute</a> -- $60</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/1772943789?tag=gamespot-promos-20&amp;tag=gamespot-buybutton-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Mr. Mega Man</a> -- $14</li></ul><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-microsd-express-card-deals-nintendo-switch-2-samsung-sandisk-amazon-walmart/1100-6530578/">Walmart Has 512GB Switch 2 MicroSD Express Card For $65</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-switch-2-restock-launch-week-buying-guide-major-retailers-walmart-target-best-buy/1100-6531967/">Nintendo Switch 2 Restocks - Where To Buy The New Console</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/playstations-dualsense-edge-ps5-controller-is-on-sale-for-its-best-price-yet/1100-6531846/">DualSense Edge PS5 Controller Drops To Best-Ever Price For Days Of Play</a></li>                          <li>         <span>